<p class="quiet">For established patients, Dr. Daftary is available by telephone 24/7 at 254-753-3646. When Dr. Daftary does take time off, our clinic Nurse Practitioner, Patricia Tatum, will be available to assist you. Our priority is to be open and available when our patients need us.</p>

