<h2>Allergy Study Programs</h2>

<p>Our office regularly participates in clinical research studies specific to allergy and asthma medications. Depending on the study protocol, participants are evaluated by medical exam and may receive study medication with ongoing evaluations. Participants are usually compensated for their time as a study participant. If interested in finding out more about our current clinical research studies, please call our office at 254-753-3646.</p>

